
Harness = Risk Department
         + Compliance Team
         + Audit Team
         + Trading Desk Controls
The agent can recommend trades.
The harness decides whether the trade is allowed.
This perfectly demonstrates:
"Agents focus on tasks. Harnesses focus on constraints."
________________________________________
What I'll Build
TradeGuard Harness
Input
{
  "portfolio_value": 250000,
  "cash_available": 50000,
  "risk_profile": "Moderate",
  "request": "Buy $40,000 NVDA"
}
Agent
Analyzes:
{
  "recommendation": "BUY",
  "ticker": "NVDA",
  "amount": 40000,
  "confidence": 0.91
}
Harness
Evaluates:
✓ Risk limits
✓ Concentration limits
✓ Compliance rules
✓ Portfolio allocation
✓ Confidence threshold
✓ Market volatility
Final decision:
{
  "status": "REJECTED",
  "reason": "Position concentration exceeds limit"
}
